        </item>
        <item>
            <title>微軟新 Surface 大幅提升可維修性，零件刊載 QR Code、清晰標示螺絲種類與位置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e6%96%b0-surface-%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%af%e7%b6%ad%e4%bf%ae%e6%80%a7-%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e5%88%8a%e8%bc%89-qr-code%e3%80%81%e6%b8%85%e6%99%b0%e6%a8%99/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e5%25be%25ae%25e8%25bb%259f%25e6%2596%25b0-surface-%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25b9%2585%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%258d%2587%25e5%258f%25af%25e7%25b6%25ad%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e6%2580%25a7-%25e9%259b%25b6%25e4%25bb%25b6%25e5%2588%258a%25e8%25bc%2589-qr-code%25e3%2580%2581%25e6%25b8%2585%25e6%2599%25b0%25e6%25a8%2599</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e6%96%b0-surface-%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%af%e7%b6%ad%e4%bf%ae%e6%80%a7-%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e5%88%8a%e8%bc%89-qr-code%e3%80%81%e6%b8%85%e6%99%b0%e6%a8%99/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 10:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1226057</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日 Microsoft 發布針對企業市場的全新 Surface Pro 10 和 Surface Laptop 6。這兩款裝置的賣點在於大大提升了維修便利性。兩款手提電腦引入了一項創新維修方式：內部零件上貼有 QR 碼，令超過十種關鍵零件的識別、更換都變得更容易。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/00_m-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/00_m-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/00_m-1.jpg 1120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/01-22-666x580.jpg" alt="" width="666" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/01-22-666x580.jpg 666w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/01-22.jpg 1033w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 666px" /></p><p>在 Surface Pro 10 中，用戶能夠輕鬆更換的部件包括顯示屏模組、可拆卸的 SSD、電池、包含處理器和 RAM 的主機板、Surface Connect 端口、散熱模組、咪高風模組、SSD 蓋子、揚聲器、外殼、前置和後置攝像頭、電源按鈕和音量按鈕以及支架。而 Surface Laptop 6 也不例外，支援更換的零件包括顯示屏組件、鍵盤、SSD、電池、主板、Surface Connect 端子、散熱模組、音頻插孔、揚聲器、觸控板和支架等。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/glbfuw-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/glbfuw-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/glbfuw.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>機身內部設計有大量提示讓修理變得更方便，例如螺絲標籤，每個零件顯示使用哪種螺絲批，還有螺絲的數量。另一方面每個可更換零件都刊載有 QR 碼，用戶可打開更換該零件的説明書。</p><p>Microsoft 更與知名電子產品維修資訊網站 iFixit 合作推出專用修理工具。廠商積極提升產品可維修性，可減少廢棄物和鼓勵產品再利用。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107592/microsoft-surface-pro-10-laptop-6-repairability-servicing-qr-codes-screw-features">The Verge</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e6%96%b0-surface-%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%af%e7%b6%ad%e4%bf%ae%e6%80%a7-%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e5%88%8a%e8%bc%89-qr-code%e3%80%81%e6%b8%85%e6%99%b0%e6%a8%99/fun-tech/">微軟新 Surface 大幅提升可維修性，零件刊載 QR Code、清晰標示螺絲種類與位置</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
